All firmware dependencies are managed via PlatformIO's lib_deps in platformio.ini.
No local lib/ subdirectories are required.

Dependencies:
  knolleary/PubSubClient@^2.8.0     — MQTT client
  mikalhart/TinyGPSPlus@^1.0.3      — NMEA sentence parser for GNSS
  electroniccats/MPU6050@^1.3.0     — MPU-6050 accelerometer/gyroscope

ESP32 built-ins used (no extra install needed):
  driver/twai.h    — TWAI (CAN bus) controller
  LittleFS         — flash filesystem for TLS certs
  Preferences      — NVS key-value store for provisioning data
  WiFiClientSecure — TLS on top of WiFi
  SD, SPI          — SD card for store-and-forward ring buffer
  HardwareSerial   — UART2 for GNSS
  Wire             — I2C for IMU
